description: Once you own this 11Second video of collaged stop-motion animation go into your basement and start the video on your device.  Leave device in basement and go back upstairs.  Lie down on the floor directly above the area that your device is in the basement.  Listen to the sound of the NFT playing through the floor for 11min.11sec. Try to imagine from your memory what the images are that are plying on your device.  Try to send empathy to your device.  Go back downstairs, get your device, watch the video one time through and say "I OWN YOU SUCKER!". BUT ONLY DO THIS IF YOU ARE THE OWNER.
